                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 21.704,
                                "byte_start": 80000,
                                "byte_stop": 166831,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinion of the Court in 76-677, Owen Equipment and Erection Company against Kroger will be announced by Mr. Justice Stewart, and also number 77-5353, Mincey against Arizona will be announced by Mr. Justice Stewart."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 21.704,
                        "stop": 105.92,
